oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Tom Paxton in Concert - Tape 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of Tom Paxton (musician) live in concert. The tape is persummed to be have been recorded at Penn. State. The recording is from an unidentified date. Tape is labeled two of three.
